Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.98,0:00:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.12,0:00:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我是昴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我是蒂安娜{\fnSimHei}·{\r}蘭斯特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.31,0:00:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我是高町薇薇歐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.98,0:00:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,本次Blu-ray Box發售！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.22,0:00:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,作為影像特典
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.48,0:00:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我們特別客串於特典中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.71,0:00:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,在無印　A's　StrikerS的三套Box中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.24,0:00:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,各開設了一個小專欄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.82,0:00:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,請大家多多捧場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.67,0:00:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,請多多捧場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,首先是第一個專欄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.09,0:00:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,小劇場　「假想系列」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.86,0:00:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,本欄目含有續作A's的豪爽劇透
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.13,0:00:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,尚未觀看TV版或劇場版A's的觀眾請特別小心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.98,0:00:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,大家準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.74,0:00:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那就開始吧
